text: Derevnya fermy 3 Sakmarskogo sovkhoza () is a rural locality (a village) in Sakmarsky Selsoviet, Zianchurinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 194 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 79 km from Isyangulovo, 8 km from Arsyonovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Zianchurinsky District
title: Derevnya fermy 3 Sakmarskogo sovkhoza
